query: Show me upside potential and committed revenue by region
sql:
SELECT
    SUM(q.upside_potential) AS total_upside_potential, SUM(q.committed_revenue) AS total_committed_revenue, q.region
FROM cisco_stage_app.qtd_commit_upside AS q
    LEFT
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.linearity_metrics AS lm
    ON q.region = lm.region
    LEFT
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.metrics AS m
    ON q.region = m.region
    LEFT
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.funnel_metrics AS fm
    ON q.region = fm.region
GROUP BY q.region
